cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.DS 

The paper deals with deep neural networks and their training on large datasets, which are common topics in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper specifically focuses on image classification benchmarks, which falls under the computer vision sub-category. The use of active learning methods and ensembles also suggests a potential fit for the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
